casebody.data:
Jan B. HAMILTON, petitioner,
v.
Don BIRD, et al. No. 16-7538. Supreme Court of the United States March 20, 2017.

*1341Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit is dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
